nodes.text: Viqui was a female Human captain who was part of the Taris Resettlement Initiative made by the Galactic Republic during the Cold War.
During this period Viqui was stationed at Waypoint Station Aurek as commanding officer.
Viqui was created for Star Wars: The Old Republic, a massively multiplayer online role-playing game released by BioWare on December 20, 2011 and may be encountered by Republic players.
